last_episode_to_air.name: Cursed
last_episode_to_air.overview: Diabolical spirits torture and taunt their unsuspecting targets. A mother and daughter become the terrified victims of a family curse, a teen boy is attacked by an unseen force and a young girl senses an evil presence hiding in her closet.

name: My Paranormal Nightmare
overview: Are ghosts and demons dwelling among us? The Fourman Brothers, a family of paranormal investigators, investigate four hauntings, including a demonic entity, a murderous specter, a dangerous force, and a dark presence in this documentary series.
